@errors {400: [Bad request](https://techdocs.akamai.com/application-security/reference/400). Invalid request body or URL parameter input., 403:[Forbidden](https: //techdocs.akamai.com/application-security/reference/403). You don't have access to match targets in this security configuration., 404: [Not found](https://techdocs.akamai.com/application-security/reference/404). Security configuration version wasn't found.}
