@errors {403:[Forbidden](https: //techdocs.akamai.com/application-security/reference/403). You are not authorized to use this API., 404: [Not found](https://techdocs.akamai.com/application-security/reference/404). The `onboardingId` was not found., 500:[Conflict](https: //techdocs.akamai.com/application-security/reference/500). Retrieving certificate challenges failed.}

